import React from "react";
import { Form, Button } from "react-bootstrap";

function AboutMe() {
  return (
    <Form className="px-4">
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Label className="">About Me</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control 
          placeholder="Headline"
          name="Headline"
          type="text"
          required
        />  
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Label className="sr-only">Description</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control 
          as="textarea" 
          className="m-auto" 
          
          rows="1" 
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Button type="submit">Save</Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default AboutMe;
